  "ai_usage": "Use for product/feature pages and 'what's new' showcases. The core is one CSS grid where each tile sets its own grid-column/grid-row span — mix large feature tiles with small stat tiles for rhythm. Keep tiles to one idea each. Recolor via --accent. Replace placeholder tiles with images/charts. Responsive: the grid collapses to fewer columns on small screens.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/bento-showcase.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Bento Grid — Product Showcase</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"bento-showcase\",\n  \"title\": \"Bento Grid — Product Showcase\",\n  \"summary\": \"An Apple-style bento product page: a modular grid of varied tiles (feature, stat, image, quote, chart) each sized to its content.\",\n  \"description\": \"The bento grid — modular tiles of different spans, popularized by Apple keynote slides — is the defining layout of the mid-2020s. This is a full product/feature page built around one large, characterful bento: a hero tile, spanning feature tiles, a stat tile, a mini-chart, a testimonial, and a CTA tile, on a clean light canvas.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"product\", \"landing\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"bento-grid\", \"modular\", \"product\", \"light\", \"apple-style\", \"2026-trend\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (CSS Grid).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Pure CSS grid + hover lifts + IntersectionObserver reveals. The chart is CSS bars. No images or libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Semantic structure, headings per tile, focus-visible, reduced-motion safe. Charts need text alternatives when populated with real data.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"grid-template / spans\", \"description\": \"Tile sizing via grid-column/row span\", \"default\": \"4-col, 140px rows\" },\n    { \"name\": \"--accent\", \"description\": \"Accent + chart color\", \"default\": \"#ff5c39\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Dark bento (swap tokens)\", \"Rearrange spans for a different rhythm\", \"Drop real screenshots into image tiles\"],\n  \"related\": [\"bento-grid\",\"card-lift\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for product/feature pages and 'what's new' showcases. The core is one CSS grid where each tile sets its own grid-column/grid-row span — mix large feature tiles with small stat tiles for rhythm. Keep tiles to one idea each. Recolor via --accent. Replace placeholder tiles with images/charts. Responsive: the grid collapses to fewer columns on small screens.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#f4f4f5;--tile:#ffffff;--ink:#0a0a0b;--muted:#6b6b72;--line:#e6e6ea;--accent:#ff5c39;--accent2:#7c5cff;--r:22px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:\"SF Pro Display\",system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.5}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.3rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:72px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;align-items:center;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;font-size:.92rem}\n  .links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}\n  .btn{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-radius:999px;padding:.55rem 1.1rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem}\n  .head{text-align:center;padding:3rem 0 2.4rem}\n  .head .kick{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.78rem}\n  .head h1{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5.5vw,3.8rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1.05;margin:.5rem 0}\n  .head p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.15rem;max-width:46ch;margin:0 auto}\n  .bento{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);grid-auto-rows:150px;gap:14px;padding-bottom:3rem}\n  .t{background:var(--tile);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:1.5rem;overflow:hidden;position:relative;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}\n  .t:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}\n  .t h3{margin:0 0 .3rem;font-size:1.15rem;letter-spacing:-.01em}.t p{color:var(--muted);margin:0;font-size:.92rem}\n  .hero{grid-column:span 2;grid-row:span 2;background:linear-gradient(150deg,#1a1a1f,#2a2540);color:#fff;border:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between}\n  .hero .big{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1}\n  .hero .chip{align-self:flex-start;background:rgba(255,255,255,.14);border-radius:999px;padding:.3rem .8rem;font-size:.78rem}\n  .wide{grid-column:span 2}.tall{grid-row:span 2}\n  .stat .n{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1}\n  .accent{background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--accent),#ff9472);color:#fff;border:none}\n  .accent h3,.accent p{color:#fff}.accent p{opacity:.9}\n  .violet{background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--accent2),#a78bfa);color:#fff;border:none}.violet h3,.violet p{color:#fff}.violet p{opacity:.9}\n  .chart{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:7px;height:62px;margin-top:.8rem}\n  .chart i{flex:1;background:var(--accent);border-radius:5px 5px 0 0;opacity:.85}\n  .quote{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.quote p{color:var(--ink);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:500}\n  .img1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fbbf24,#f97316)}.img2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#34d399,#0ea5e9)}\n  .cta{grid-column:span 2;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border:none;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .cta h3{color:#fff;font-size:1.4rem}.cta .btn{background:#fff;color:var(--ink)}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  footer{text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;padding:2rem 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.bento{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.hero,.wide,.cta{grid-column:span 2}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.t{transition:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav>\n      <div class=\"brand\">◧ Cassette</div>\n      <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Features</a><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a><a href=\"#\">Customers</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Try it free</a></div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <header class=\"head\">\n      <p class=\"kick\">Cassette 4.0</p>\n      <h1>Everything, in its right place.</h1>\n      <p>A workspace organized the way your brain actually works.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"bento\">\n      <div class=\"t hero reveal\">\n        <span class=\"chip\">★ New release</span>\n        <div><div class=\"big\">Capture, connect, and create — all in one canvas.</div></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"t wide reveal\"><h3>⚡ Blazing fast</h3><p>Opens in under 50ms. Search across everything instantly.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"t stat reveal\"><div class=\"n\">128k</div><p>teams onboard</p></div>\n      <div class=\"t accent reveal\"><h3>Made to delight</h3><p>Tiny details, everywhere.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"t img1 tall reveal\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Feature image\"></div>\n      <div class=\"t reveal\"><h3>📈 Grows with you</h3><div class=\"chart\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i style=\"height:40%\"></i><i style=\"height:60%\"></i><i style=\"height:50%\"></i><i style=\"height:78%\"></i><i style=\"height:90%\"></i><i style=\"height:100%\"></i></div></div>\n      <div class=\"t quote wide reveal\"><p>“It replaced five tools and made our week 30% calmer.”</p><p style=\"color:var(--muted);margin-top:.4rem\">— Priya N., Head of Ops</p></div>\n      <div class=\"t violet reveal\"><h3>🔌 200+ apps</h3><p>Connect your whole stack.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"t img2 reveal\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Feature image\"></div>\n      <div class=\"t cta reveal\"><h3>Ready to tidy up your workday?</h3><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Start free →</a></div>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Cassette · Designed in the open.</footer>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.1});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
